casebody.data:
James E. McWILLIAMS, petitioner,
v.
Jefferson S. DUNN, Commissioner, Alabama Department of Corrections, et al. No. 16-5294. Supreme Court of the United States March 6, 2017.

Motion of the petitioner for appointment of counsel granted, and Stephen B. Bright, Esquire, of Atlanta, Georgia, is appointed to serve as counsel for the petitioner in this case.
